---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Project Detail" 
  description="Panorama Heights Residence - A luxury residential project by Ultraction General Contracting featuring sustainable design and breathtaking views."
>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <section class="project-header relative h-[70vh] min-h-[500px] flex items-end overflow-hidden mb-20">
      <div class="project-hero-image absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-center bg-cover opacity-0 animate-zoom-fade" style="background-image: url('/api/placeholder/1400/800')"></div>
      <div class="project-hero-overlay absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-t from-dark via-dark/70 to-dark/30"></div>
      <div class="project-title-container relative z-10 w-full px-10 pb-10">
        <span class="project-category inline-block px-5 py-2 bg-primary text-light text-sm rounded-full mb-4 transform translate-y-8 opacity-0 animate-slide-up">Luxury Residential</span>
        <h1 class="project-title text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-5 text-light transform translate-y-8 opacity-0 animate-slide-up animation-delay-300">Panorama Heights Residence</h1>
        <p class="project-location text-xl opacity-80 mb-4 transform translate-y-8 opacity-0 animate-slide-up animation-delay-500">Vancouver, British Columbia</p>
        <div class="project-stats flex flex-wrap gap-8 mt-8 transform translate-y-8 opacity-0 animate-slide-up animation-delay-700">
          <div class="project-stat flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="stat-icon w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
                <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="stat-value font-semibold text-primary">8,500 sq ft</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-stat flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="stat-icon w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="stat-value font-semibold text-primary">14 months</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="project-stat flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="stat-icon w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 2.69l5.66 5.66a8 8 0 1 1-11.31 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="stat-value font-semibold text-primary">LEED Platinum</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="project-content grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mb-20">
      <div class="project-description col-span-2">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6">
          Panorama Heights Residence represents the pinnacle of luxury sustainable living, perched on the scenic slopes of North Vancouver with breathtaking views of the city skyline, mountains, and ocean. This bespoke residential project seamlessly blends contemporary architecture with the natural surroundings while incorporating cutting-edge sustainable technology.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6">
          Ultraction General Contracting led the entire development process, from initial concept through design collaboration, engineering, and construction. Our team worked closely with the renowned architectural firm Greenwood & Associates to create a home that would not only stand as a testament to luxury but also as a beacon of environmental responsibility.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6">
          The structure features a cascading design that follows the natural contours of the hillside, with each level offering expansive outdoor living spaces. Floor-to-ceiling windows throughout maximize natural light and showcase the panoramic vistas, while carefully selected materials including local stone, sustainable timber, and brushed metals create a harmonious balance between modern sophistication and organic warmth.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6">
          Beyond aesthetics, this residence boasts an impressive array of sustainability features that earned it LEED Platinum certification. A geothermal heating and cooling system, 12kW solar array, rainwater harvesting system, and state-of-the-art home automation for energy management come together to create a net-zero energy home that doesn't compromise on luxury or comfort.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90 mb-6">
          Interior spaces flow seamlessly from one to another, with an open-concept design that emphasizes both functionality and elegance. Custom millwork, artisanal finishes, and integrated smart home technology throughout provide the perfect balance of beauty and convenience for the homeowners.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="project-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-content bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 sticky top-24">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-white/10">Project Details</h3>
          <ul class="project-details-list">
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Client</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">Private Residence</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Location</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">North Vancouver, BC</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Project Size</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">8,500 sq ft</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Completion</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">June 2024</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Duration</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">14 months</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Architect</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">Greenwood & Associates</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4 border-b border-white/5">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Certification</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">LEED Platinum</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-between py-4">
              <span class="detail-label font-medium opacity-70">Awards</span>
              <span class="detail-value font-semibold">Design Excellence 2024</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="key-features py-20 bg-white/[0.02] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="section-pattern absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23b38728\" fill-opacity=\"0.4\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 inline-block relative">
            Key <span class="text-primary">Features</span>
            <span class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-primary -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full"></span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto opacity-80">
            Innovative elements that define this exceptional residence
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Geothermal System</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              A state-of-the-art geothermal heating and cooling system that harnesses the earth's natural temperature to maintain perfect comfort while reducing energy consumption by up to 70%.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Solar Integration</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              A 12kW solar array seamlessly integrated into the roof design provides clean, renewable energy that powers the home's electrical needs and feeds excess back to the grid.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h.5A2.5 2.5 0 0020 5.5v-1.65" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Water Management</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              Advanced rainwater harvesting and greywater recycling systems reduce water consumption by 65%, supporting landscape irrigation and non-potable water needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Smart Home System</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              Comprehensive home automation controls lighting, climate, security, entertainment, and energy management through intuitive interfaces and voice commands.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Biophilic Design</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              Architecture that connects occupants with nature through living walls, natural materials, abundant daylight, and seamless indoor-outdoor transitions.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="feature-card-top absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[5px] bg-gradient-primary"></div>
            <div class="feature-icon w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Advanced Security</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-80">
              Comprehensive security system with biometric access control, surveillance cameras, motion detection, and remote monitoring for peace of mind.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="project-gallery py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">
          <span class="text-primary">Project</span> Gallery
        </h2>
        
        <div class="gallery-grid grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-2 gap-4 h-[600px] opacity-0 transform translate-y-12 transition-all duration-1000" id="galleryGrid">
          <div class="gallery-item col-span-8 row-span-2 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/800/600" alt="Exterior view" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="gallery-overlay absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Exterior View</h3>
                <p class="text-light opacity-80">Front facade with landscaping</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="gallery-item col-span-4 row-span-1 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/400/300" alt="Living room" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="gallery-overlay absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Living Room</h3>
                <p class="text-light opacity-80">Open concept with panoramic views</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="gallery-item col-span-4 row-span-1 rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/400/300" alt="Kitchen" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="gallery-overlay absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end">
              <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">Gourmet Kitchen</h3>
                <p class="text-light opacity-80">Custom cabinetry and premium appliances</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="model-viewer-section py-24 bg-white/[0.02] relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="section-pattern absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(var(--primary) 2px, transparent 2px); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
      
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">
          <span class="text-primary">3D</span> Architectural Model
        </h2>
        
        <div class="model-container relative h-[500px] bg-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden perspective-[1000px]">
          <div class="model-placeholder absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
            <div class="model-cube transform-style-preserve-3d animate-rotate">
              <div class="cube-face cube-front bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">FRONT</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cube-face cube-back bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">BACK</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cube-face cube-right bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">RIGHT</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cube-face cube-left bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">LEFT</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cube-face cube-top bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">TOP</span>
              </div>
              <div class="cube-face cube-bottom bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold">BOTTOM</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary mt-8 mb-2">Interactive 3D Model</h3>
            <p class="max-w-md opacity-70 text-center">
              Experience the Panorama Heights Residence in immersive 3D. Explore every detail of this architectural masterpiece.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="testimonial-section py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="testimonial-container bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-12 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 relative">
          <div class="quote-icon absolute top-8 right-8 text-primary/20 text-8xl font-serif">"</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-8 relative z-10">
            Working with Ultraction General Contracting exceeded all our expectations. Their attention to detail, craftsmanship, and ability to bring our vision to life was truly remarkable. From start to finish, the entire process was seamless and the result is beyond what we imagined.
          </p>
          <div class="testimonial-author flex items-center">
            <div class="author-avatar w-16 h-16 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
              <img src="/api/placeholder/64/64" alt="Client" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-xl text-primary">James & Sarah Thompson</h4>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-70">Homeowners</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="next-projects py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">
          Explore More <span class="text-primary">Projects</span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="next-projects-grid grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="next-project-card relative h-[350px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/600/800" alt="Commercial project" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="next-project-overlay absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark to-transparent transform translate-y-4 opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
              <span class="next-project-category inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary text-light text-xs rounded-full mb-2">Commercial</span>
              <h3 class="next-project-title text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-1">Modern Office Complex</h3>
              <a href="#" class="text-primary font-medium hover:text-accent transition-colors">View Project →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="next-project-card relative h-[350px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/600/800" alt="Multi-family project" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="next-project-overlay absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark to-transparent transform translate-y-4 opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
              <span class="next-project-category inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary text-light text-xs rounded-full mb-2">Multi-Family</span>
              <h3 class="next-project-title text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-1">Eco-Friendly Apartments</h3>
              <a href="#" class="text-primary font-medium hover:text-accent transition-colors">View Project →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="next-project-card relative h-[350px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-3 hover:shadow-2xl group">
            <img src="/api/placeholder/600/800" alt="Hospitality project" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
            <div class="next-project-overlay absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark to-transparent transform translate-y-4 opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-y-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
              <span class="next-project-category inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary text-light text-xs rounded-full mb-2">Hospitality</span>
              <h3 class="next-project-title text-xl font-semibold text-light mb-1">Luxury Beach Resort</h3>
              <a href="#" class="text-primary font-medium hover:text-accent transition-colors">View Project →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
